title: 102: Suspicious Celebrity Deaths ft. Lizzie & Ellie | Crew Biscuits Ep. 2
description:
On this week's Crew Biscuit, Lizzie & Ellie dig into the suspicious circumstances surrounding the deaths of Marilyn Monroe & Lina Morgana. Did Marilyn know too much about aliens & the crash at Roswell? Did Lady Gaga sacrifice Morgana to achieve success and secure her place in the illuminati? Find out on this week's Crew Biscuit.
